      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against the NASA rotor benchmark and lid-driven cavity test cases. Order of accuracy for the species transport equation used to carry the hemolysis index was confirmed at 1.97 on a manufactured solution, consistent with second-order spatial discretisation."
