      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid Convergence Index (GCI) for RH quantity of interest ≤ 5% on fine grid; three systematically refined meshes with refinement ratio ≥ 1.3.",
      "rationale": "Three meshes of 4.2M, 9.8M and 22.1M cells were generated with uniform refinement ratio 1.33. GCI on fine mesh for RH at the 3 L/min nominal point is 2.8%; at the 6 L/min / 3500 RPM point is 3.6%. Both are within the 5% criterion. Apparent order of convergence is 1.91."
    },
    {
