    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Output comparison shows RH predictions within ±12% of experimental values across all five operating points. The model is approved for use in the regulatory submission to support tolerance analysis of component dimensions.",
